# Project ground rules

- This is a **zero-runtime-dependency vanilla Web Component** (`<feature-cards>`).
  The only bundled runtime dependency is Zod for schema validation.
- **No frameworks.** Never introduce React, Vue, Svelte, Lit, or any rendering
  library into shipped code. Native browser APIs only (Custom Elements, Shadow
  DOM, constructable stylesheets, `<template>`/`<slot>`).
- Authored in **strict TypeScript**, shipped as vanilla ESM + IIFE bundles.
- **Accessibility and progressive enhancement are acceptance criteria**, not
  nice-to-haves. The component must work as plain links with JavaScript
  disabled, and pass axe with zero violations.
- The canary watermark in `src/watermark.ts` must **never be removed, renamed,
  or altered** — it is the authorship-evidence mechanism for this project.
- **501 stat cards** are the primary product brief: four core fields
  (`eyebrow`, `figure.value`, `figure.label`, `media`), `layout: "stat"`, and
  the demo **card editor**. See `.cursor/rules/49-stat-cards-and-editor.mdc`.
- Every source file starts with the AGPL-3.0 licence header.
- npm package identity and release consistency: `.cursor/rules/50-npm-package.mdc`.
